---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/main.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Enerama Environmental Technologies"
  description="Enerama Environmental Technologies privacy policy. Your data rights, our practices, and GDPR compliance information."
  keywords="privacy policy, data protection, GDPR, enerama privacy"
  canonicalPath="/privacy-policy"
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="text-white py-20" style="background-color: #0B3D4C;">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-200">Your privacy and data protection are important to us</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8"><strong>Last Updated:</strong> January 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4" style="color: #1B3A6B;">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Enerama Environmental Technologies ("we," "us," or "our") collects information that you provide directly to us when you contact us, request information, or engage with our services. This may include your name, email address, company information, and project details.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4" style="color: #1B3A6B;">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">We use the information we collect to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-4">
          <li>Respond to your inquiries and provide requested information</li>
          <li>Process and fulfill project requests</li>
          <li>Communicate with you about our products and services</li>
          <li>Improve our website and services</li>
          <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4" style="color: #1B3A6B;">3. Information Sharing</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to third parties. We may share information with trusted service providers who assist us in operating our website or conducting our business, subject to confidentiality agreements.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4" style="color: #1B3A6B;">4. Data Security</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal information against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4" style="color: #1B3A6B;">5. Your Rights</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Under applicable data protection laws (including GDPR for European clients), you have the right to:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-4">
          <li>Access your personal information</li>
          <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
          <li>Object to processing of your data</li>
          <li>Request data portability</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4" style="color: #1B3A6B;">6. International Data Transfers</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          As a company with operations in the USA, Switzerland, and Türkiye (and a representation office in Azerbaijan), your information may be transferred to and processed in these countries. We ensure appropriate safeguards are in place for such transfers.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4" style="color: #1B3A6B;">7. Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or wish to exercise your rights, please contact us at:
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:info@enerama.com" class="hover:opacity-80" style="color: #E07B39;">info@enerama.com</a>
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4" style="color: #1B3A6B;">8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "Last Updated" date.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
